title: Increase demand or liquidity on Mutant
body:
Right now more mutants are created everyday, while the Y-men decrease.
This causes inbalance in the y-men / mutant pool. 
this will eventually cause the project to fail, since the availability to exchange between the offered liquidity pairs is essential. 
now to exchange about 1000 mutants to ymen will cause the price to be effected by 25%. 
If liquidity is being pulled by the imbalance of the decreasing and low supply of ymen, I am suggesting the following fixes.
choices: have a bot automatically send ymen or mutant to the pool when liquidity is going to low.
create new ways to spend Mutants or different routes. 1 suggestion would be to burn 10000 (medium rare) or 100000 (rare) mutants to buy NFT.
create demand for Mutant in different ways just then to buy Y-men if liquidity issue can not be solved
author: 0x1Fa4823613Fb2424cbDab225FC1eEfe3Bd293c84
